snippet.title: My Friendly Neighborhood Trailer
snippet.description:
You're a repairman here to solve the mystery at an old TV station. This was a friendly kid's show so why are the puppets acting strangely? My Friendly Neighborhood is a survival-action horror game that will give you some good scares while making friends. 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1574260/My_Friendly_Neighborhood/

Game made by John and Evan Szymanski
https://twitter.com/Ducky_Szymanski

Game published by DreadXP
twitter https://twitter.com/DreadXP_
